{"tid":1026659,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★高人一等？】猝死行山男證實為立法會秘書處保安　梁君彥：將助其家人度難關","createTime":"2019-02-18T09:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T05:17:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d8bbf377ce163da1aa9c4d3cbc7d9bd6913c03","tid":1026659,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:32:14.000Z","msg":"一名姓陳45歲的男子上周六於油塘魔鬼山行山不適昏迷，送院後不治。立法會主席梁君彥今(18日)證實，該名男子為秘書處保安員，對事件感難過，強調會為其家人提供一切可行協助，幫他們度過難關。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上周六(16日)，該名45歲姓陳的保安員在油塘魔鬼山行山，至中午12時許，他行至一食水配水庫對開時感到不適，自行報警後暈倒。政府飛行服務隊直升機到場，將事主送到東區醫院搶救，惜於2時55分證實不治。警方經初步調查，相信事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。據悉，死者生前患有糖尿病。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/296199/猝死行山男證實為立法會秘書處保安-梁君彥-將助其家人度難關\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F296199%2F%E7%8C%9D%E6%AD%BB%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%B1%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E7%82%BA%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E8%99%95%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5-%E5%B0%87%E5%8A%A9%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%BA%A6%E9%9B%A3%E9%97%9C&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgDmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=de29d4f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/296199/猝死行山男證實為立法會秘書處保安-梁君彥-將助其家人度難關</a>"},{"pid":"c3510b20b6a3949c0d70372fa8982da6d3b4acdb","tid":1026659,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"地盤咁多工業意外唔見佢理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652bd96ddcd41cad1955954f341c4084f1060adc","tid":1026659,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3cd1a8ee596aae00d7b36a96eda123821c0cb1","tid":1026659,"uid":37661,"like":9,"dislike":0,"sco